EventDescription: Developers Day 2020 is a great opportunity to learn more about Google Developers Products like AMP, PWA, Firebase, Android and Google Maps Platform. The events also give one a chance to meet developer advocates and engineers who work on these products and ask them any questions one might have. GDG Jalandhar is once again hosting a workshop named “Developers Day 2020”. The conference aims at bringing together Google technology enthusiasts of all experience levels, from new users to core developers. 'Developers Day 2020' provides a platform for companies who are looking for developers to interact with and get involved with the developer community of Google as well as a great chance to connect with so many talented developers will join us from around the world.
